<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Vaccination Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 10px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
        .highlight { background-color: #ffeb3b; padding: 5px; border-radius: 3px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üêæ Vaccination Reminder</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello!</h2>
            <p>This is a friendly reminder that <strong>{{petName}}</strong> has an upcoming vaccination appointment.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight">
                <h3>Vaccination Details:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Pet:</strong> {{petName}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Vaccine:</strong> {{vaccineName}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Scheduled Date:</strong> {{scheduledDate}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Days Until Due:</strong> {{daysUntilDue}}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Please make sure to schedule an appointment with your veterinarian if you haven't already.</p>
            <p>Keeping your pet's vaccinations up to date is crucial for their health and wellbeing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated reminder from your Pet Care System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>